00:04:11.020 --> 00:04:12.900
Slut, I'll surely kill you.

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:14.420
Thach!

00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:15.480
Dirty ass!

00:04:15.640 --> 00:04:16.840
- Leave me.
- Leave her!

00:04:17.200 --> 00:04:18.180
Get the f*ck out of me.

00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:18.580
Brother!

00:04:18.580 --> 00:04:19.640
