00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.260
OK?

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:19.120
Uhm.

00:05:19.340 --> 00:05:20.440
One...

00:05:21.460 --> 00:05:22.680
Two...

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:24.440
Three.

00:05:25.820 --> 00:05:26.600
Phuc.

00:05:28.420 --> 00:05:29.520
I caught you! 

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.840
I lose so fast.

00:05:31.860 --> 00:05:32.760
