00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:35.200
If you're this excellent, forget the whole thing and play again!

00:05:35.900 --> 00:05:36.880
It can't!

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:39.340
I've caught you and even called your name.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.520
You wouldn't have if I hadn't fallen.

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.800
I can always catch you.

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:45.900
Sure. I dare you.

00:05:46.140 --> 00:05:47.100
Let's play again.

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:48.940
Are you blindfolding yourself?

00:05:49.700 --> 00:05:51.380
Yes, I'm covering my eyes.

00:05:52.420 --> 00:05:54.060
OK. Let's begin.

00:05:54.460 --> 00:05:55.500
I'm searching.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.980
